<lb n="11" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> paḷa śaraṇāgata vajraprākāra lōkaikakaḷpadru
<lb n="12" break="no"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> ḍa maṁḍaḷikalalāṭapaṭṭa vairigharaṭṭa subhaṭa rā
